comment: Sweet, Carmel. Smells good, no burn, menu does not have alcohol, guessing under 100. Smooth, I like it.
Very sweet. Caramel butterscotch, and vanilla notes. Very smooth.

N - Fruit/banana, cereal, vanilla

T - full, malty, toasted oak, toffee

F - ash, butterscotch

Included in a Bourbon Charity blind tasting. Voted number three for me out of 5 AZ whiskies. 

Sampled at home.
